OL,3,CPolitician apologises and admits he is
OL,4,Cfacing criminal charges
OL,6,FHe added: "Given that this matter is
OL,7,Fsubject to judicial proceedings, I
OL,8,Fwill not be making any further comment
OL,9,Fat this time - except to confirm that
OL,10,FI will cooperate fully with the
OL,11,Fprocess."
OL,13,FDeputy Ozouf extended his apologies as
OL,14,Fone of the island's most experienced
OL,15,Fpoliticians.
