OL,3,CPolitician apologises and admits he is
OL,4,Cfacing criminal charges
OL,6,FHe said: "As a long-serving member of
OL,7,Fthis Assembly, fully cognisant of the
OL,8,Fneed to uphold the highest standards
OL,9,Fof conduct in both public and private
OL,10,Flife, I express regret that this
OL,11,Fmatter has arisen and how it may
OL,12,Freflect on this Assembly.
OL,14,F"I express a similar regret to my
OL,15,Fconstituents in St Saviour."
OL,17,FThe specific charges faced by Deputy
OL,18,FOzouf are not known.
